ScenarioDataSource.SQL_Text:
SELECT DISTINCT Max (Concat (CDHDR.UDATE, CDHDR.UTIME)) OVER (PARTITION BY CDPOS.TABKEY ) AS DATETIME,
                CDPOS.CHNGIND,
                KNA1.*
FROM   "SAPECD"."CDHDR" CDHDR
       INNER JOIN "SAPECD"."CDPOS" CDPOS
         ON CDPOS.OBJECTCLAS = CDHDR.OBJECTCLAS
            AND CDPOS.CHANGENR = CDHDR.CHANGENR
            AND CDPOS.TABNAME = 'KNA1'
       INNER JOIN "SAPECD"."KNA1" KNA1
         ON CDPOS.OBJECTCLAS = 'DEBI'
            AND CDPOS.OBJECTID = KNA1.KUNNR
            AND CDPOS.TABNAME = 'KNA1'
            AND CDPOS.TABKEY = Concat (KNA1.MANDT, KNA1.KUNNR)
WHERE  CDHDR.OBJECTCLAS = 'DEBI'
       AND ( CDHDR.UDATE >= '20240903' )
ORDER  BY KNA1.KUNNR

SELECT DISTINCT Max (Concat (CDHDR.UDATE, CDHDR.UTIME)) OVER (PARTITION BY CDPOS.TABKEY ) AS DATETIME,
                CDPOS.CHNGIND,
                KNA1.*
FROM   "SAP_TABLES"."PUBLIC"."CDHDR" CDHDR
       INNER JOIN "SAP_TABLES"."PUBLIC"."CDPOS" CDPOS
         ON CDPOS.OBJECTCLAS = CDHDR.OBJECTCLAS
            AND CDPOS.CHANGENR = CDHDR.CHANGENR
            AND CDPOS.TABNAME = 'KNA1'
       INNER JOIN "SAP_TABLES"."PUBLIC"."KNA1" KNA1
         ON CDPOS.OBJECTCLAS = 'DEBI'
            AND CDPOS.OBJECTID = KNA1.KUNNR
            AND CDPOS.TABNAME = 'KNA1'
            AND CDPOS.TABKEY = Concat (KNA1.MANDT, KNA1.KUNNR)
WHERE  CDHDR.OBJECTCLAS = 'DEBI'
       AND ( CDHDR.UDATE >= '20240903' )
ORDER  BY KNA1.KUNNR
